Package main.java.objects

Class Oven

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Thread
main.java.objects.Oven
All Implemented Interfaces:
Runnable
public class Oven extends Thread
This is the main class in the system which represents a single oven worker. Oven extends a thread for the purpose of having multiple ovens work simultaneously.
